去到哪个城市都要好好珍惜～打一下,参观一下…

Nei Nei和Max都会唱了,也超级爱听…
这次Alan Walker来上海一定要到现场感受😍

Enjoy China and have a blast 💪😍 🇨🇳 

#alanwalker #faded #shanghai #brunei #alanwalkermusic

Merry Christmas 🎄☃️❤️🎉🤩

#merrychristmas #christmastree #brunei #china #uae

End the year right💪

We did it!
Creating tons of great memories and never stop making dreams come true…
Yes, everything happens for a reason and truly grateful for all the good and bad making us stronger and wiser. 
Ciao 2023😊💪👋 

2023过得太充实了…
有很多的挑战,也有很多的喜悦…
生命本来就不会一帆风顺…
懂得感恩和珍惜才能做到人生赢家…
每年都希望争取有个美好的结尾结束一年的挑战…
我们算做到了😊💪
感恩有我很爱的家人,朋友还有你们一直的陪伴❤️
2023,谢谢你👋

#goodbye2023 #brunei #china #感恩

Fly High 2024. 
是时候再次勇敢起飞💪
A new year, a new you!
Happy Healthy 2024🎉👍

#2024 #happynewyear #lifeisbeautiful #flyhigh #新年快乐

Magnificent Abu Dhabi

It’s all about the WOW factor in this perfect city thrill for family like us 😍 

-Ride the 240km/hr world’s fastest rollercoaster at Ferrari World
-Team up with Batman at Warner Bros.
-Marvel at the beauty of The Sheikh Zayed Grand Mosque
-Splashy fun slides and rides at Waterworld
-Educational adventure on marine life at Seaworld
-The most incredible and dramatic desert scenery
-Louvre Art Gallery iconic architecture 

There’s just too many Heart-pumping adventures and never-ending fun all day, all night. 
来到阿布扎比,我是不是很入乡随俗

世界最快240km/hr的过山车🎢

再次大开眼界🤩❤️👍

Thank you @YasIsland for inviting us to this whole new world ultimate family vacation😍👍🙌
